    <briefdescription>
<para>A tensor plus its reference to its parent tensor. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="structTTL__sub__tensor" kindref="compound">TTL_sub_tensor</ref> contains both the logical dimensions of a tile as well as its physical mapping to memory.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>TTL_scope</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The scope of the creation can be TTL_global or TTL_local </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>const_1</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The const name to place after the prefix - should be empty or const_ </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>location</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The location of the tensor - should be ext or int </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>type</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The type of the tensor - should be any valid c type </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>const_2</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The const type to create - should be empty or const </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
